  "notes": "Primary data from the official RFEG club page (REAL LA MANGA CLUB, id=542), which lists the Oeste recorridos with per-hole par, hcp and meters for Blancas/Amarillas/Azules/Rojas, each rated for both genders. Stroke index is identical across all tees. Cross-checked against The Social Golfer's West Course yellow-tee scorecard: pars and stroke indexes match exactly; distances match RFEG Amarillas except hole 14 (TSG 302 vs RFEG 290; TSG also labels the values as yards though they are clearly meters). RFEG taken as authoritative. Note: some aggregator sites describe the West as par 73, but the official RFEG rating card is par 72 (36 out / 36 in). All internal checks pass: SI is a permutation of 1-18, pars sum to 72, and each tee's per-hole meters sum exactly to its RFEG total (5714/5521/5130/4724)."
